{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1683299255.117633", "card_id": "Q_598539429", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 270}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "西北工业大学邵典老师发布「不正经招生指南」爆火，如何看待邵典老师发布的招生贴，是否推荐报考？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "最近西北工业大学导师邵典在知乎发了自己的「不正经招生指南」一下子爆火，链接如下：邵典：西北工业大学邵典老师 - 不正经招生指南 如何看待其新颖的招生风格？其真实学术水平如何？是否推荐大家报考？ 相关链接："}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b1ed9cb262ef41cf2f8bd24ce07eb296_xll.jpg?source=32738c0c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1368 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/598539429"}, "text_tag_area": {"text": "邵典亲自答", "font_color": "GYL01A", "background": "GYL01A"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Is7GiiMeXjbwuEAMaCDk1Mjg5Mjg3IMnTuaIGMBY4xgdAAHIJNTk4NTM5NDI5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1683299255.119195", "card_id": "Q_599231157", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 123}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "全球首例！北京成功完成非人灵长类动物介入式脑机接口试验，具有哪些重要意义？从动物试验抵达临床还有多久？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "5 月 4 日，全球首例非人灵长类动物介入式脑机接口试验在北京取得成功。试验在猴脑内实现了介入式脑机接口脑控机械臂，对推动脑科学领域研究具有重要意义，标志着我国脑机接口技术跻身国际领先行列。 什么是脑机接口？全球正在推进研发的脑机接口有哪些种类？从动物试验抵达临床还有多远的路要走？全球首例！北京成功完成非人灵长类动物介入式脑机接口试验"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b763752d083d57d0031a8e75b2f06e52_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "334 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/599231157"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Is7GiiMeXjbwuEAMaCDk1NDQzMDgyIIGL06IGMA848gJAAXIJNTk5MjMxMTU3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1683299255.1204836", "card_id": "Q_599295788", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b7